[I] Games for the Linux Console

[T] The programs in this distribution are re-implementations of games 
[T] for the Linux console. Included please find three games:
[T]    * cblocks -- sliding-block puzzles
[T]    * cmines -- minesweeper
[T]    * csokoban -- sokoban 
[T] The games make use of the Linux console font and mouse support to 
[T] improve the user interface.

